    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level specimen of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a perfectly indexed VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering razor-sharp throttle response through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This chassis has been meticulously sorted with documented subframe reinforcement and VAC coated rod bearings, ensuring total mechanical integrity. The limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution, while the suspension geometry remains factory-precise with zero bushing deflection. Finished in a flawless coat with an interior free of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who values technical perfection and kinematic purity.",
