      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, seeing only fair-weather weekend use. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; the body is entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior remains in showroom state, with no visible wear on the seat bolsters, pedals, or steering wheel, and it still retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized Porsche centers, and I possess a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt and the original window sticker. With only 8,500 miles on the clock, this car has never been tracked or driven in the rain. It comes equipped with the Premium Package Plus, 20-inch Carrera S wheels, and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a collector-grade example that will satisfy the most detail-oriented buyer seeking a turn-key, flawless driving experience.",
